{{Infobox video game | title = Ylands | image = Ylands_Cover.jpg | developer = [[Bohemia Interactive]] | publisher = Bohemia Interactive | engine = [[Unity (game engine)|Unity]] | platforms = [[Microsoft Windows]] | released = | genre = [[Survival game|Survival]] | modes = [[Single-player video game|Single-player]], [[Multiplayer video game|multiplayer]] | composer = }}
'''''Ylands''''' is a [[sandbox game]] in development by [[Bohemia Interactive]].
==Gameplay== Developers describe ''Ylands'' as "sandbox exploration adventure and a platform for making custom games". The game has been compared to ''[[Minecraft]]'' and features a built-in editor that allows players to make their own scenarios.<ref name="Arma Devs Launch 5v5 FPS Project Argo’s Free Prototype">{{cite web|last1=O'Connor|first1=Alice|title=Arma Devs Launch 5v5 FPS Project Argo’s Free Prototype|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/11/01/arma-developers-release-free-project-argo-prototype/|website=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|accessdate=15 April 2017|date=1 November 2016}}</ref>
''Ylands'' gives players freedom in creation and modification of the countryside. Players can create their own character and choose an environment. Environments include temperate, tropical, winter etc. The editor allows the player to create their own scenario which allows gameplay set in different eras such as Wild West, medieval Europe or a steampunk world and others. Developers stated that they do not want to make any boundaries for players.<ref name="Čeští tvůrci fenoménů Arma a DayZ ohlásili novou hru ve stylu Minecraftu">{{cite web|last1=Brabec|first1=Andrej|title=Čeští tvůrci fenoménů Arma a DayZ ohlásili novou hru ve stylu Minecraftu|url=http://bonusweb.idnes.cz/ylands-bohemia-interactive-cesky-minecraft-fk8-/Novinky.aspx?c=A151116_172656_bw-novinky_anb|website=iDNES.cz|accessdate=15 April 2017|date=16 November 2015}}</ref>
==Development== The game was announced on 24 November 2017 when the Alpha version of the game was released on Bohemia Interactive's website.<ref name="Bohemia Interactive ukazují své Ylands - Hrej.cz">{{cite web|last1=Dřevíkovský|first1=Vojtěch|title=Bohemia Interactive ukazují své Ylands|url=http://www.hrej.cz/novinky/2015/11/13/bohemia-interactive-ukazuji-sve-ylands-37821/|website=Hrej.cz|accessdate=15 April 2017}}</ref><ref name="Nová česká hra Ylands si to namířila mezi Minecraft a jiné survival hry s otevřeným světem - Games.cz">{{cite web|last1=Homola|first1=Adam|title=Nová česká hra Ylands si to namířila mezi Minecraft a jiné survival hry s otevřeným světem|url=http://games.tiscali.cz/oznameni/nova-ceska-hra-ylands-si-to-namirila-mezi-minecraft-a-jine-survival-hry-s-otevrenym-svetem-268725|website=Games.cz|accessdate=15 April 2017|language=cs}}</ref> The game was formally announced worldwide on 1 November 2016 when it became part of project ''Bohemia Incubator''.<ref>{{cite web|title=Bohemia Interactive formally announce 'Ylands', will support Linux later|url=https://www.gamingonlinux.com/articles/bohemia-interactive-formally-announce-ylands-will-support-linux-later.8454|website=GamingOnLinux|accessdate=15 April 2017|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Arma Devs Launch 5v5 FPS Project Argo’s Free Prototype"/> The [[Steam (Valve)|Steam]] version of the game was announced on March 9 2017 and released on December 6 2017.<ref>"[https://ylands.com/faq Frequently Asked Questions]", Ylands. Retrieved May 16, 2017.</ref> According to game's Steam page, the full version of the game will be released 6-8 months after its release on Steam.
